{
  "stem": "4693.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the second trial, as I told you, came to nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I met, in Warsaw, she found me a cousin of mine who's husband was senator of Poland, a member of Polish senate.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And during the First World War, he was one of the principles of the Polish underground army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He'd died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had a heart attack in the start of the-- at the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw him in Lviv.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, he was a very bright guy, and he was a head of a group in, before the Second World War, of a Polish group, leftist group-- not a socialist group, so-called [POLISH], a part of town.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And under him, was in his group the later the prime minister of Poland, the deputy president of-- and the vice president of Poland, a number of others.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And with her, we went to see this vice president of Poland, Schwalbe was his name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Seeing him were two reasons-- one was to arrange something for my wife, to get her out of Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Second one, we, together with them, had a farm, a large farm, a holiday place, as well, not far from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this was taken over by the government.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we wanted to-- to get it back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we approached this vice president of Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he promised that he will do something about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was later returned, but then he was nationalist again, as I found out later, much later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, he called immediately the foreign minister, and while we were there-- Modelevsky was his name-- and he told him to take immediate steps to get my wife out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he came with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
